message.body: Hey Caitlin - I'm back in PA! Are you back too? I'll be around this weekend to ride, should we figure out a schedule?
Yes I am back. And yes. Lets meet this weekend and figure out a schedule. Would it work if I rode on Saturday and you rode on Sunday this week?
I am planning to. Is that ok?
Yup - I'm hacking dollar here and there too so I might see you.
